{"tid":44660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒生被發現當眾小便","createTime":"2016-12-18T12:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T04:59:58.000Z","uid":18348,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a0f413173541c95db60f70d0b88055957d3fb4","tid":44660,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"蘇格蘭地方副議長燒生 監督關閉公廁 卻被發現當眾小便<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaus.ee/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/18137-1o0pa8k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F18137-1o0pa8k.jpg&h=61364906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北澤郡 North Lanarkshire &ndash; 當地議會的副議長燒生 Jackie Burns 日前被發現尷尬情況，就是竟然被發現當眾小便。<br />\n而最硬膠的是，這位燒生負責的工作，就是監督議會早前通過，關閉當地公廁的預算，更令這個罰款40鎊的罪案顯得額外尷尬。<br />\n<br />\nSouth Lanarkshire council&rsquo;s deputy leader, who oversaw the closure of public toilets in his area, has been caught publicly urinating by police.<br />\n<br />\nLabour councillor Jackie Burns was caught in the act in Hamilton town centre and given a fixed penalty notice of &pound;40 by police on Saturday.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2015/12/burns-toilet/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2015%2F12%2Fburns-toilet%2Famp&d=zI7nI0FtvnPeIT9ky4u6pUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=98a145ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2015/12/burns-toilet/amp</a>"},{"pid":"e415cd3e285e8478327fdc82b2ba0f040bf55dde","tid":44660,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe7265a4102bde09cf3a7cd90c6d83bd0ce58c8","tid":44660,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Vf6MtZ0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVf6MtZ0.gif&h=f0f23eb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"417389ba2728b1509eddc586e82734bf3772d656","